STATE
v.
Delauno Montrez COREY. No. 539P05. Supreme Court of North Carolina. September 30, 2005. Geoffrey W. Hosford, Wilmington, for Delauno Montrez Corey. Seth Edwards, District Attorney, for State.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 29th day of September 2005 by Attorney General for Temporary Stay:

"Motion Allowed by order of the Court in conference this the 30th day of September 2005."
